Cut @pumpkin{1} into wedges and place in pressure cooker.

In a pan, heat @butter{85 g}, @ginger{6 cm}, @lemon juice{30 ml}, @cinammon stick{1}, and @sugar{125 g} for ~{1 min}.

Drizzle sauce onto pumpkin and add optionally some @pumpkin oil{}. Cook for ~{40 min}. Serve hot.